OL,3,CTwo more teens charged after others
OL,4,Cwere stabbed during disorder in
OL,5,CSmethwick
OL,7,FTwo more teenagers have been charged
OL,8,Fwith attempted murder after others
OL,9,Fwere stabbed during a disorder in
OL,10,FSmethwick.
OL,12,FAn 18-year-old man was arrested at the
OL,13,Fweekend as part of enquiries into
OL,14,Farmed violence in Foundry Lane last
OL,15,FTuesday evening (26 May).
OL,17,FEdson Silva was charged with two
OL,18,Fcounts of attempted murder and
OL,19,Fpossession of a knife.
OL,1,W~+$ ~sh7}h7sj5 ~{4~k4k4          G1/4
