OL,3,CTwo more teens charged after others
OL,4,Cwere stabbed during disorder in
OL,5,CSmethwick
OL,7,FHe was remanded to appear before
OL,8,FBirmingham Magistrates Court today
OL,9,F(1st June).
OL,11,FIt comes after we arrested and charged
OL,12,Fa 17-year-old boy, who cannot be named
OL,13,Fdue to his age, with the same offences
OL,14,Fon Friday. He appeared at court on
OL,15,FSaturday.
OL,17,FPolice have now charged three teens in
OL,18,Fconnection with the disorder at around
OL,19,F9.30pm.
